// items
// satchel
COPY ~baldurianbarhop/Fully Booked/itm/BFSCB.ITM~ ~override~
SAY NAME1 ~Satchel of the Avowed~
SAY NAME2 ~Satchel of the Avowed~
SAY DESC ~Satchel of the Avowed
Crafted from purple-dyed leather and trimmed with white fur, this enchanted satchel is standard issue among the Avowed of Candlekeep. Designed to aid in the secure transport of commissioned copies and rare texts, it allows its wielder to carry several books without burdening them with their weight. It also shields the tomes within from weather and wear: a necessity for those tasked with safeguarding Candlekeep's ever-growing trove of knowledge.

STATISTICS:

Weight: 2~

